Package com.smjourney.entity

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Destructible
    Implemented in any object that is considered destructible.
    Moveable
    Implemented in any object considered moveable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttackShip
    This ship type is characterized by high attack, low shields, medium capacity, and medium thrusters.
    BeamShip
    This ship type is characterized by its ability to refuel nearby ships.
    Debris
    An inert Entity that serves no purpose other than to take up space in the battle sequence.
    Entity
    A general Entity, and object with an ID and one or more parts, that can be placed on a group of cells within a map to function.
    EntityPartition
    A part of a whole Entity.
    EntityTracker
    This class contains static methods to track specific entities on a map, given a Map parameter that is updated constantly outside of the context of this tracker.
    LargeDebris
    Large-sized debris with a size of 3.
    MediumDebris
    Medium-sized debris with a size of 2.
    Mothership
    This ship type is characterized by being the center of command for the fleet.
    ScoutShip
    This ship type is characterized by very high thrusters, low shields, low capacity, and medium attack.
    Ship
    A functioning starship that operates with its own shields, energy capacity, thruster power, and attack power.
    SmallDebris
    Small-sized Debris with a size of 1.
    SupportShip
    This ship type is characterized by high shields, low attack, high capacity, and low thrusters.
